Class NonAdmin_Controller

java.lang.Object
controllers.NonAdmin_Controller
public class NonAdmin_Controller extends Object
Controller for the non-admin user main view. Lists albums and provides create/delete/rename/open/search/logout actions for the active user.

Similar to MainController but used by the renamed NonAdmin UI FXML.

Author:
Zach
